Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)

Package: sing-gateway
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, sing-box, nftables, iproute2, procps, jq, systemd
Description: inert Debian companion integration for sing-box TProxy gateway mode
 sing-gateway installs a small wrapper around tproxy_ctrl.sh that discovers
 local sing-box configuration, validates it, and explicitly enables optional
 sing-box.service lifecycle hooks for TProxy gateway setup and cleanup.
